  ShadowColor: {x: 1.000000, y: 1.000000, z: 1.000000, w: 1.000000}
  ShadowDensity: 1.000000
  Text: |-
    Air Hockey – Connected Lens
    
    To get started, preview the Lens on two Spectacles devices using Lens Studio.
    
    One player can initiate the game to begin the session.
    
    Once the game starts, you can play Air Hockey using your Bitmoji avatars. Your Bitmoji and your opponent’s Bitmoji will load automatically. Until both avatars are fully processed, a placeholder version will be displayed.
    
    To play, select the paddle and move it by pinching, or manipulate it directly from a close distance.
    
    For clarity and development purposes, the colliders are intentionally enabled and visible to help you better understand how the Lens functions.  For testing take advantage of the double preview in the editor. Control the paddle with the cursor. You will only see your avatar. 
